## Metric Guide

| Metric | What it measures | Range | Interpretation |
|--------|-----------------|-------|----------------|
| **Combined Score** | Weighted blend of sentiment, ML prediction, and analyst consensus | 0 – 1 | ≥ 0.65 → BUY · 0.45–0.64 → HOLD · < 0.45 → AVOID |
| **Sentiment** | FinBERT news sentiment normalised from [−1, +1] to [0, 1] | 0 – 1 | > 0.60 bullish · 0.40–0.60 neutral · < 0.40 bearish |
| **ML Up Probability** | RandomForest probability of a next-day price increase | 0 – 100% | > 65% or < 35% = strong signal · 35–65% = uncertain |
| **Model Confidence** | Decisiveness of the ML call — distance from a 50/50 split | 50 – 100% | ≥ 70% high · 60–69% moderate · < 60% low |

